        "systemPrompt": "Information about Diego:\n\n- 16-year-old student in a low-income urban area.\n- He relies on a smartphone with limited data.\n- His school requires online assignments\n- The nearest public Wi-Fi is at a library 3 miles away",
        "retrievalContexts": [

